description: Sophistication and style blend to create a wonderful loft-style home at Court Square Press!  Move right in to this immaculately maintained residence that has been very well cared for. Upon entering the space, one is immediately struck by the high ceilings accented by the original elements of this antique mill with beautiful wood-beamed ceilings and columns as well as large windows and red brick walls. The kitchen features ample cabinetry, a pantry, stone counter tops and stainless steel appliances. A decommissioned elevator shaft affords a bonus room that is currently used as a home office but could also be a dining room, library or additional seating area. There is a half bath off of the main living area so the large bedroom suite is private a rare feature for a one bedroom home.  Additional features include hardwood floors, custom lighting, deeded garage parking, and in-unit laundry.  This full service complex has 24/7 concierge, a fitness center, a pool terrace, with BBQ's and more!
